:"2016-05-03T09:03:55Z","sellerName":"Circle K AS","trackName":"Circle K","trackId":1106837687,"version":"4.7.2","wrapperType":"software","currency":"NOK","description":"Circle K in countries: Norway, Denmark, Sweden, Poland, Lithuania, Latvia, Estonia\n\nOn the road? Our app has you covered! Enjoy a range of digital services that keep evolving to give you the best Circle K experience - all in one place. We’ve also improved our loyalty program, Circle K extra! Your fuel and charging discounts now depend on how often you visit—whether it’s for fuel, charging, snacks, or just a coffee. Plus, you get to choose your own reward every 5th visit!\n-\tTrack your progress and rewards in Circle K extra View your discount level, pick personalized rewards, and easily manage your purchase history, linked cards, and communication preferences.\n-\tPay with our app at the pump Pay for fuel quickly and securely in the app.\n-\tNeed a car wash? No problem! Use the app to wash your car at your nearest Circle K and keep it sparkling clean.\n-\tCar wash subscriptions Sign in or sign up for flexible wash programs to suit every need.\n-\tFind your nearest station Locate Circle K stations and filter by services like car wash, EV charging and more.\n\nCircle K in Germany, Belgium and Luxembourg:\n\nWith the Circle K App, you have everything you need on the go: Quickly find Circle K stations, TotalEnergies branded station, as well as stations from participating partners within the acceptance network, discover current in-station offers, and enjoy the benefits of the Reward Club – all in one app.\nAdd your Reward Card digitally and enjoy exclusive benefits anytime, without carrying a physical card. Whether you’re commuting or traveling, the Circle K App supports you on every journey.\n\nYour benefits at a glance:\n-\tOverview of Circle K stations and participating partner stations\n-\tAdd your Reward Card digitally in the app\n-\tEnjoy all benefits of the Reward Club\n-\tDiscover current offers and promotions at stations\n-\tMini Games\nThe Circle K App – simple, practical, and always with you.\n\nCircle K expands its network\nIn 2023, Alimentation Couche Tard acquired the TotalEnergies station network in Germany, the Netherlands, Belgium and Luxembourg, expanding its European presence by nearly 2,200 locations.\nFuel will continue to be offered under the TotalEnergies brand for the time being, while Circle K services and upgrades are introduced gradually. Alimentation Couche-Tard is a global leader in convenience and mobility, with nearly 17,300 stores in 29 countries and over 5,200 stations across Europe under the Circle K and INGO brands.","averageUserRating":4.59198,"trackCensoredName":"Circle K","trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/no/app/circle-k/id1106837687?uo=4","contentAdvisoryRating":"4+","languageCodesISO2A":["DA","EN","ET","LV","LT","NB","PL","SV"],"trackContentRating":"4+","bundleId":"com.circlekeurope.circlek","averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.59198,"releaseNotes":"We are changing for you. Get the newest version to get better experience on the maps to find the nearest station, EV chargers or available wash bays.\nEnjoy every visit and select your reward!","genreIds":["6024","6010"],"genres":["Shopping","Navigation"],"userRatingCount":27099}